# C# Style — always applied

Follow the canonical standards in the shared folder (single source of truth):

- C# style & naming → [`agent-standards/20-csharp-style.md`](../../agent-standards/20-csharp-style.md)
- Async & concurrency → [`agent-standards/30-async.md`](../../agent-standards/30-async.md)
- Security baseline (OWASP) → [`agent-standards/70-security-owasp.md`](../../agent-standards/70-security-owasp.md)
